headline: FactSet Research Systems (FDS) Integrates MarketAxess AI-Powered Data Into Workstation
summary: FactSet Research Systems (FDS) has recently integrated MarketAxess' AI-powered CP+ data into its workstation, making it the sole provider of such capabilities in a terminal desktop environment. This integration is designed to provide users with real-time bond pricing and insights on a vast array of securities, centralizing financial data and enhancing trade execution.
